# Hardware

Webconverger works with **almost any standard x86 PC hardware** that meets
[Firefox's minimum
requirements](http://www.mozilla.com/en-US/firefox/system-requirements.html).

# Customisation

<http://webconverger.com> is a UK & Singapore registered company that powers
this project.  The money generated through customisations is the fuel.

In the past there were bespoke customisations where an ISO was generated and the
turnaround was a day or two.

Now there is a [customisation
service](http://config.webconverger.com/faq). From version 12, a downloaded
Webconverger should boot into this service and allow customers an easy user
experience to setup and subscribe.

